<TITLE> Joy visits father's grave </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Rangpur, May 16 (bdnews24.com) Prime minister Sheikh Hasina's son Sajib Wazed Joy on Saturday offered prayers at his father's grave in Fatehpur in Pirganj Upazila in Rangpur. Joy drove to Dr M A Wazed Miah's grave shortly before midday. State minister for home Tanjim Ahmed, state minister for local government Jahangir Kabir Nanak, whip Mirza Azam and MP Sheikh Helal accompanied him tour. The nuclear scientist died in Dhaka on May 8 after prolonged illness. bdn
